Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class ReliabilityVisualizationTest

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.ReliabilityVisualizationTest
class ReliabilityVisualizationTest extends Object
Tests the class ReliabilityVisualization to make sure the reliability analysis methods are set up properly. In these tests, Jackie wrote the tests for testCreateColumnHeader(). Matt wrote the tests for testCreateHeader() and testCreateVisualizationData(). Jackson wrote the test for testCreateTitle().
Author:
Jackie Mills, Matt Boenish, Jackson Grant
